{
  "stem": "11998.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I always watched the-- the guards and the kapo, making sure that, when they-- when they ever watched me, I was working.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the minute they turned their-- their eyes or their face, I would stop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the only way you could survive on a-- on a construction site.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to-- to an extent, it became sort of ridiculous, because we were carrying big railroad tracks and-- you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and was about that far shorter-- And my Shoulder was that far shorter below-- below the man that was carrying in front and back of me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was just holding it up, really, not doing very much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that-- that old man, he took a liking to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he started giving me jobs to do, like count the [INAUDIBLE], count the prisoners, or cook his meal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he would bring me a-- a bag of potatoes, raw potatoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he'd tell me to make a fire, especially when it got to the-- in the fall, and the potatoes were harvest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would make a fire, and I'd roast the potatoes for him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, always a couple got lost in the-- in the fire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he didn't mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- he was-- he was OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I could help my father with bread and soup all through the--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we slept in the same barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes, when he was on night shift and I was on day shift, that-- we-- we'd pass each other, us, going in and out of the camp, or coming into the factory.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I would make sure that I was on the right-hand side and he was on the right-hand side, so that I could throw him a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
